			<div type="container2" xml:lang="en">
				<head type="container2">Death of My Grandmother</head>
				<pb n="001" />
				<note><unclear>needs to be checked</unclear></note>
				<lg n="stanza_title">
					<lg>
						<l>Lethe, The River of Forgetfulness</l>
					</lg>
					<lg>
						<l>When my grandmother was crossing the Lethe,</l>
						<l>When she hadn’t yet stepped into the river</l>
						<l>And hadn’t yet regained consciousness</l>
						<l>as she had lost her footing, from washed ashore driftwood</l>
						<l>hooked on the hem of her skirt</l>
						<l>by force of her old habit</l>
						<l>which made her walk straight</l>
						<l>she strengthened herself, drew herself up</l>
						<l>and thus stepped into the river.</l>
						<l>The water was cool, the water was soft</l>
						<l>The forest was stretched along the river bank</l>
						<l>And everything was so familiar to her</l>
						<l>That she started to think:</l>
						<l>Am I crossing the Iori River</l>
						<l>Am I still going to look for my lost cow</l>
						<l>In the forest across the river?</l>
						<l>She has not even glanced at me</l>
						<l>My eyes all darkened in tears</l>
						<l>I am unable to see,</l>
						<l>Her crossing to the other shore,</l>
						<l>Disappearing</l>
						<l>Vanishing into the mist.</l>
					</lg>
					<lg>
						<l>Afterlife</l>
					</lg>
					<lg>
						<l>When my Grandmother arrived in the afterlife</l>
						<l>She was met by kindred spirits:</l>
						<l>Those who had died either by a bullet,</l>
						<l>Or passed away by black death,</l>
						<l>Deceased either by betrayal</l>
						<l>Or even poisoned by love</l>
						<l>Only Nato the widow has not come</l>
						<l>To meet my grandma</l>
						<l>Because even now she seemed too busy</l>
						<l>Even here to join in the feast</l>
						<l>As in her own life -</l>
						<l>Even here</l>
						<l>She could be found in the forest</l>
						<l>Collecting brushwood</l>
						<l>For her orphans</l>
					</lg>
					<lg>
						<l>NO DATE</l>
					</lg>
				</lg>
